-- African Integration Could Lead to Regional Bonds, Kenyan Central Bank Says
-- B y   E m i l y   B o w e r s
-- 2010-10-27T11:26:42Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-27/african-integration-may-lead-to-regional-bonds-kenya-s-ndung-u-says.html
Better integration among African
regional groupings means “nothing stops us from raising
infrastructure bonds across the region,” said Njuguna Ndung’u,
governor of Kenya’s central bank.  “Partnerships must start from the regional level, then the
global level,” he told an African Development Bank conference
in Gammarth, Tunisia, today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Emily Bowers at 
